      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん！？　ま、まぁ、そんなところです\nというか、なんで寮にいるんですか？",
      "startTime": 24.033333687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "音楽番組の収録まで時間があるから、戻って来たのよ\nついでに、こころに予定の確認をしようと思って",
      "startTime": 31.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、明日早朝からお仕事ですよね、覚えてますよ\nあれ！？　それより莉央さん、可愛い髪型ですね～",
      "startTime": 39.989911898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokkrroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
