      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんは、『リズノワにとって』立派なリーダーです\nこころが保証しますから。これからも胸を張って下さい",
      "startTime": 141.3333404541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_53_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、センターの方はいつか、こころがもらっちゃい\nますけどねっ。それくらい、こころも頑張りますから",
      "startTime": 149.6666737874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
